# {{ project_name }}

A LangGraph agent built with Open LangGraph Platform.

## Quick Start

```bash
# Install dependencies
uv pip install -e .

# Set up environment
cp .env.example .env
# Edit .env with your API keys

# Run development server
olg dev
```

## Project Structure

```
{{ project_name }}/
├── graphs/
│   └── agent.py      # Your agent graph
├── open_langgraph.json  # Configuration
└── .env              # Environment variables
```
